{"type":"freeform","cover":{"titleText":"","subTitleText":"","presenterText":"","dateText":"","logos":[]},"section":{"sectionText":"","smallerSectionText":""},"freeform":{"content":[[{"type":"text","span":4,"stretch":true,"fillArea":true,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"grey","placeholderInvisible":false,"placeholderStretch":true,"placeholderHeight":50,"useFigureAdditionalScale":false,"figureAdditionalScale":1,"imgHeight":300,"imgFit":"inside","imgStretch":true,"hideFigureCaption":false,"hideFigureSubCaption":false,"hideFigureFootnote":false,"markdown":"Les enquêtes montrent une progression régulière de la couverture Penta 3 entre 2005 et 2011, atteignant un pic d’environ 90 %, suivie d’une baisse puis d’une stabilisation autour de 90 % en 2024.

Les données issues du DHIS2 (en gris) indiquent des niveaux légèrement supérieurs.

L’extrapolation à partir de la dernière enquête (en rouge) projette une couverture de 96 % en 2025, confirmant une reprise progressive."},{"type":"figure","stretch":true,"fillArea":false,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"none","placeholderInvisible":false,"useFigureAdditionalScale":true,"figureAdditionalScale":0.8,"presentationObjectInReportInfo":{"id":"3e3230cb-ad9e-48b9-b3ce-7bd01255d20b","moduleId":"m004","selectedReplicantValue":"penta3","replicateBy":"indicator_common_id","isDefault":true},"hideFigureFootnote":false,"hideFigureCaption":false}]],"useHeader":true,"headerText":"Estimations de la couverture basées sur les données HMIS et les enquêtes nationales"}}

{"type":"freeform","cover":{"titleText":"","subTitleText":"","presenterText":"","dateText":"","logos":[]},"section":{"sectionText":"","smallerSectionText":""},"freeform":{"content":[[{"type":"text","span":4,"stretch":true,"fillArea":true,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"grey","placeholderInvisible":false,"placeholderStretch":true,"placeholderHeight":50,"useFigureAdditionalScale":false,"figureAdditionalScale":1,"imgHeight":300,"imgFit":"inside","imgStretch":true,"hideFigureCaption":false,"hideFigureSubCaption":false,"hideFigureFootnote":false,"markdown":"L’analyse des tendances de la couverture en CPN4 montre une progression modérée, passant d’environ 40 % en 2005 à 50 % en 2016, puis atteignant 68 % en 2023.

Les données issues du DHIS2 (en gris) indiquent des niveaux légèrement inférieurs, autour de 65 % en 2023 et proches de 70 % en 2025, donc en deçà des estimations des enquêtes.

L’extrapolation à partir de la dernière enquête (en rouge) projette une couverture de 74 % en 2025, confirmant la tendance haussière observée dans les enquêtes."},{"type":"figure","stretch":true,"fillArea":false,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"none","placeholderInvisible":false,"useFigureAdditionalScale":true,"figureAdditionalScale":0.8,"presentationObjectInReportInfo":{"id":"3e3230cb-ad9e-48b9-b3ce-7bd01255d20b","moduleId":"m004","selectedReplicantValue":"anc4","replicateBy":"indicator_common_id","isDefault":true},"hideFigureFootnote":false,"hideFigureCaption":false}]],"useHeader":true,"headerText":"Estimations de la couverture basées sur les données HMIS et les enquêtes nationales"}}

{"type":"freeform","cover":{"titleText":"","subTitleText":"","presenterText":"","dateText":"","logos":[]},"section":{"sectionText":"","smallerSectionText":""},"freeform":{"content":[[{"type":"text","span":4,"stretch":true,"fillArea":true,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"grey","placeholderInvisible":false,"placeholderStretch":true,"placeholderHeight":50,"useFigureAdditionalScale":false,"figureAdditionalScale":1,"imgHeight":300,"imgFit":"inside","imgStretch":true,"hideFigureCaption":false,"hideFigureSubCaption":false,"hideFigureFootnote":false,"markdown":"L’analyse des tendances de couverture pour le vaccin Penta 1 montre que les enquêtes indiquent une couverture élevée et stable, autour de 90 % entre 2005 et 2023.

Les données issues du DHIS2 (gris) suggèrent des niveaux tres proches.

L’extrapolation à partir de la dernière enquête (rouge) projette une couverture de 100 % en 2025."},{"type":"figure","stretch":true,"fillArea":false,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"none","placeholderInvisible":false,"useFigureAdditionalScale":true,"figureAdditionalScale":0.8,"presentationObjectInReportInfo":{"id":"3e3230cb-ad9e-48b9-b3ce-7bd01255d20b","moduleId":"m004","selectedReplicantValue":"penta1","replicateBy":"indicator_common_id","isDefault":true},"hideFigureFootnote":false,"hideFigureCaption":false}]],"useHeader":true,"headerText":"Estimations de la couverture basées sur les données HMIS et les enquêtes nationales"}}

{"type":"freeform","cover":{"titleText":"","subTitleText":"","presenterText":"","dateText":"","logos":[]},"section":{"sectionText":"","smallerSectionText":""},"freeform":{"content":[[{"type":"text","span":4,"stretch":true,"fillArea":true,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"grey","placeholderInvisible":false,"placeholderStretch":true,"placeholderHeight":50,"useFigureAdditionalScale":false,"figureAdditionalScale":1,"imgHeight":300,"imgFit":"inside","imgStretch":true,"hideFigureCaption":false,"hideFigureSubCaption":false,"hideFigureFootnote":false,"markdown":"L’analyse des tendances de la couverture vaccinale pour le BCG montre que les enquêtes indiquent des niveaux élevés et stables, avoisinant 90 à 95 % entre 2005 et 2024.

